edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configurationSpecification
Class BlockTypeInstance

java.lang.Object
  edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configurationSpecification.BlockTypeInstance

public class BlockTypeInstance
extends java.lang.Object

The BlockTypeInstance class represents the layout of a block type for a particular FPGA part. Each part should have as many BlockTypeInstances as there are BlockTypes in the family. The column layout is represented as a list of BlockSubTypes.
